subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution ( Fig. 2 ). Known from the western North Atlantic [Gulf of Mexico and Caribbean Sea, Bahamas , off French Guiana and Suriname ( Mayer 1974 ; Fujii 1983 ; McEachran and Fechhelm 2005 )]; off Angola , southeastern Atlantic (present study); off Vietnam , South China Sea, ( Abramov 1992 ); Galápagos Islands, eastern Pacific ( McCosker and Long 1997 ;
Okamoto et al. 2012
); and Indian Ocean [Sumatra, Western Australia, Timor Sea, off tropical east Africa, Walters Shoals ( Brauer 1906 ; Mayer 1974 ; Shcherbachev 1987 ; Allen and Cross 1989 ; Abramov 1992 ;
Williams et al. 1996
; present study)]; at depths of 120– 1100 m .
